entries.title: Radioactive capsule missing in Australia after falling off mining truck
entries.description: Australian emergency services are in a race against time to find a tiny but potentially deadly radioactive capsule that has gone missing while being transported 870 miles (1,400km) from a mine to a depot in the city of Perth.

entries.title: Scorpion: The police task force set up to tackle high murder rates, now involved in the killing of an unarmed man
entries.description: When Memphis, a city in southwest Tennessee, had a record number of homicides in 2021 for the second year in a row, many were calling for action.

entries.title: Endangered shark meat sold in Australian fish and chip shops, study finds
entries.description: Meat from endangered sharks is being served up in Australian fish and chip shops, researchers have found.

entries.title: Punched, kicked and tasered: Timeline of violent arrest of Tyre Nichols
entries.description: Tyre Nichols was punched, kicked and tasered, beaten with a baton and had pepper spray used on him during a violent arrest by police in Memphis, video footage shows.

entries.title: A region on edge: Why this is a dangerous moment for Israel and West Bank
entries.description: Make no mistake, this is a very dangerous moment for Israel and the West Bank.

entries.title: Two wounded in 'terror attack' in Jerusalem hours after deadly synagogue shooting
entries.description: Two people have been wounded in a suspected terror attack in Jerusalem, hours after a deadly shooting outside a synagogue.

entries.title: Haunting video of Tyre Nichols arrest before his death is sickening indictment of policing that night
entries.description: Of all the words used prior to prepare us, nothing spoke louder than the pictures.

entries.title: 'New clock' on police accountability after death of Tyre Nichols, says civil rights campaigner
entries.description: The US has a "new clock" on police accountability following the quick arrest and firing of five officers charged over the death of Tyre Nichols, influential civil rights campaigner Al Sharpton has said.

entries.title: Bodycam footage shows Tyre Nichols calling for his mother as he is beaten by officers before his death
entries.description: Memphis Police has released bodycam footage showing the moment Tyre Nichols called for his mother as he was beaten by five officers before he died.
